cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper discusses the intersection of computer vision and drones, specifically focusing on object detection and tracking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, since the paper deals with the use of drones, it is likely to fall under cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for visual analysis, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, since the paper deals with video analysis, it could also be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
